<br>
 Walking back through village Dawn had stopped in her hut, and changed into a pale pink dress from Greece, and around the inner side of her thigh, she had sheathed a knife, it was slender and smooth enough to be just like it was the flesh. All weapons were removed except for it, and elven boots laced tighter, so that the sheathes were gone. <br>
<br>
 Then the Amazon set back out into the village, going to the High Council meeting hut...following Hippolyte's directions, Dawn found the old map. Rolling it up, and tying a red ribbon around it, Dawn left. <br>
<br>
 Next step was to find Sartha. <p>Pyschotic injustice
Mommy made me this way
Evil and hungry
