 only to find a letter from Sartha telling her that she had went on ahead to the village, and placed the rafts in the designated spots they chose on the map.  <br>
<br>
 With that Dawn took the pigeon out of its cage, setting it on her shoulder. Fingers wound around the pink dress skirt as she hiked it up and began walking into the forest. It was time to go meet the villagers of Gargarensia...<br>
